After being asked to bat, Bangladesh totalled 139 for 8 in their 20 overs in their tri-nation series T20I match at the R. Premadasa Stadium.Liton Das was the top scorer for Bangladesh with 34 while Sabbir Rahman made 30.J. Unadkat was the pick of the Indian bowlers with 3 for 38.A short while ago, after 7 overs, India was 55 for 2.Shikhar Dhawan was 21 not out.